ive HF 160 D|HF 160 D]]-type locomotive.\n|-\n| 11\n|'' Ferret *''\n|[[File:WLLR 11, Llanfair, 2016.jpg|150px|Ferret]]\n| [[Hunslet Engine Company]]\n| 2251\n| 1940\n| 1971\n| {{nowrap|{{whyte|0-4-0|DM}}}}\n|Diesel\n| Operational\n|Previously from Admiralty Depots. Returned to service in 2015 and is used primarily as a works shunter at Llanfair.\n|-\n| 12\n|'' Joan''\n|[[File:WLLR 12, Raven Square, 2016.jpg|150px|Joan at Raven Square]]\n| [[Kerr Stuart]]\n| 4404\n| 1929\n| 1971\n| {{nowrap|{{whyte|0-6-2|T}}}}\n|Steam\n| On display\n| Originally operated in Antigua. Returned to service in 2011 with a new boiler. Out of service from 2020 following expiry of 10 year boiler ticket.\n|-\n| 14\n|'' -''\n|[[File:WLLR 14 at Castle Caereinion.jpg|150px|WLLR 14 at Castle Caereinion]]\n| [[Hunslet Engine Company]]\n| 3815\n| 1954\n| 1975\n| {{nowrap|{{whyte|2-6-2|T}}}}\n|Steam\n| On display\n| Originally operated by [[Sierra Leone Government Railway]].\n|-\n| 16\n|'' Scooby *''\n|\n| [[Hunslet Engine Company]]\n|\n| 1941\n| 1992\n| {{nowrap|{{whyte|0-4-0|DM}}}}\n| Diesel\n| Stored\n| Previously from Admiralty Depots. Rebuilt by W&LLR\n|-\n| 17\n| TSC 175\n|[[File:WLLR 17, Llanfair, 2016.jpg|150px|Diema]]\n| Diema\n|\n| 1979\n| 2004\n| {{nowrap|{{whyte|6w|DH}}}}\n| Diesel\n| Operational\n| Originally operated by [[Taiwan Sugar Railways|Taiwan Sugar Company]]\n|-\n\n|}\n<small>* = Name added by WLLR</small>\n\n===Locomotives on hire===\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n!No.\n!Name\n!Image\n!Builder\n!Works No.\n!Date built\n!Date arrived\n!Wheels\n!Type\n!Status\n!Notes\n\n|-\n| 2\n| ''Zillertal''\n|[[File:Zillertal Bahn - Steam Locomotive.jpg|150px|No 2 Zillertal]]\n| [[Krauss-Maffei|Lokomotivfabrik Krauss & Co.]]\n| 4506\n| 1900\n| 2019\n| {{nowrap|{{whyte|0-6-2|T}}}}\n| Steam\n| Operational\n| U Class, one of two locomotives built for the opening of the [[Zillertalbahn]]. Arrived in August 2019 on hire from the Zillertalbahn for approximately two years.<ref>{{cite web | title =Llanfair